data.text:
Step into the ring in 'Boxing Legends Of The Ring' on the Super Nintendo. Fight as legendary boxers, use unique moves, and compete in intense matches. Experience the excitement and challenge of classic boxing action.

Release Date: September 01, 1993

Genre: Sports
